                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#9r" facs="010">Fol. 9r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1105HolyWoman">Holy Woman</ref>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">St Mary</persName> and a sleeping man. A church stands in the background</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#64r" facs="065">Fol. 64r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1105HolyWoman">Holy Woman</ref>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">St Mary</persName> gives a blessing to a person with arms folded across chest</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#114v" facs="116">Fol. 114v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1105HolyWoman">Holy Woman</ref>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">St Mary</persName> with a net saving a mother and infant in the water</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#6v #12v #18v #27v #34r #39r #47r #56v #63v #68v #79v #90r #93r #98v #104r #115v #116r #122v" facs="008 014 020 029 035 040 048 058 065 070 081 091 094 100 105 117 124">fols. 6v, 12v, 18v, 27v, 34r, 39r, 47r, 56v, 63v, 68v, 79v, 90r, 93r, 98v, 104r, 115v, 116r, 122v</locus> (a line of alternating red and black dots)
                    </decoNote>
